`docs/design/proactive-ai-tutor-settings.md` created. Covers:

- **Data model**: `ProactivePreferences` interface replacing `ProactiveMessageSettings`, with fields for master toggle, frequency/timing (`reminderFrequency`, `maxMessagesPerDay`, `quietHours`, `preferredStudyTime`), tutor tone (5 options), notification channels (3), weak skill priority (ordered list), automation level + 3 auto-toggles, 15 category toggles, and AI enhancement
